经在应用程序徽标中的 Vudu 下方粘贴了“Fandango”。）&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;duuZGf&quot;>;Vudu...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.vudu.com/ theverge.com/2024/2/16/24075041/vudu-fandango-at-home-rebranding-new-name&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/2/16/24075041/vudu-fandango-at-home-rebranding-new-name" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/2/16/24075041/vudu-fandango-at-home-rebranding-new-name</id><author><name>克里斯·韦尔奇</name></author></entry></feed>